{
  "stem": "10818.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I did very well in high school and had the choice of maybe applying to some colleges for a scholarship or getting into practical work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And colleges that gave scholarships at that time were the seven sisters, that kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we felt that I probably-- I wouldn't be able to keep up socially with-- I mean, we just didn't have the money to afford the kind of things.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, we had no money whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If I wanted to-- I asked my father for a newspaper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said, pick up one out of a garbage can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We don't have money for this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was-- I went to a business school, of which there were many in those days, and learned steno and typing-- and I mean, these are now arcane skills-- and bookkeeping and stuff like that, for nine months.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how I could have spent nine months at this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think we were taken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, I got a job right after that, as a secretary, and started going to college at night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which college was that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hunter College, which was-- you know, it's one of the New York City system colleges and had a very good reputation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And went at night for two years, while I was working in one job, then another job and then decided to go during the daytime and get it over with.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I did my freshman year in two years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it would have taken-- I have a friend who did it, actually, all at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I finished up in the next three years, and finished up in college and got out by 1947.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in contact until Pearl Harbor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in constant contact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still have letters.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
